subject: World Cup (Skiing)
Skiing
Alpine Skiing
lead_paragraph: Lindsey Vonn failed to finish among the top three in a World Cup super-G for the first time in nearly three years when she was 18th at Bad Kleinkirchheim, Austria, on Sunday.
